  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0db3\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0d8b\u0dab, \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0da9\u0dca 19, \u0d91\u0da0\u0dca.\u0d85\u0dba\u0dd2.\u0dc0\u0dd3.  \u0dad\u0dd4\u0db1\u0db8 \u0d91\u0d9a\u0dc0\u0dbb \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Monkey flu, Covid 19, HIV All three are formed at the same time",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 36-year-old gay man in Italy was diagnosed with monkey flu, Covid-19 and HIV. The country's health department says that all three have been infected at the same time.",
        "Monkey Flu, Covid 19 and HIV are viral diseases and it is said that this is the first time that all three diseases have been found in the same person.",
        "The doctors said that this person who returned from a five-day trip to Spain had fever, sore throat, fatigue and headache after about nine days.",
        "Accordingly, when he underwent a full medical examination, he was diagnosed with monkey fever, Covid-19 and HIV. It was confirmed that he was infected. It is also said that this person has been infected with 'Covid 19' before."
      ],
